Q: o aplicatie cu titlul "MyApp" cu trei butoane aliniate orizontal: "Start" in stanga, "Settings" in centru si "Exit" la dreapta
A:
self.setWindowTitle("MyApp")
layout = QHBoxLayout()
layout.addWidget(QPushButton("Start"))
layout.addWidget(QPushButton("Settings"))
layout.addWidget(QPushButton("Exit"))
self.setLayout(layout) #end